   <mods:abstract>He is sorry for the actions of the gentleman he introduced to Jay, and
            thanks Jay for his kind treatment of the man despite the situation. He has been
            reelected as Governor, although the opposition had been strong. Jay's reappointment as
            Chief Justice will give him an opportunity to entertain Jay in Charleston, which would
            be very gratifying.</mods:abstract>
